"title": "4844: rain",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4844",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Rain as a natural phenomenon</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:10\">2SA 21:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:41\">1KI 18:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:44\">1KI 18:44</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:9\">EZR 10:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:3\">ECC 11:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:6\">ISA 4:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:54\">LUK 12:54</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:7\">HEB 6:7</a></p>\n<h3>Associated with cold weather</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:2\">ACT 28:2</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God controls the rain</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:5\">GEN 2:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:16\">JER 51:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:1\">1KI 18:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:10\">JOB 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:26\">JOB 28:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:6\">JOB 37:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:25\">JOB 38:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:8\">PSA 68:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8\">PSA 147:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:22\">JER 14:22</a></p>\n<h3>God's bounty in giving rain to Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:12\">DEU 28:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:4\">LEV 26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:14\">DEU 11:14</a></p>\n<h3>God's bounty in giving rain to all humanity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:1\">ZEC 10:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's punishment through rain and flood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:4\">GEN 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:33-Exod9:34\">EXO 9:33–9:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:17-1Sam12:18\">1SA 12:17–12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:22\">EZK 38:22</a></p>\n<h3>God's punishment through drought</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:17\">DEU 11:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:35-1Kgs8:36\">1KI 8:35–8:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:26-2Chr6:27\">2CH 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1\">1KI 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:6\">ISA 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:7\">AMO 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:17-Zech14:18\">ZEC 14:17–14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17\">JAS 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:6\">REV 11:6</a></p>\n<h2>Rain as a symbol of spiritual truth</h2>\n<h3>God's power to save</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:4\">2SA 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:8\">ISA 45:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's powerful anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:11-Ezek13:13\">EZK 13:11–13:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:12\">2SA 22:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:23\">JOB 20:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:2\">ISA 28:2</a></p>\n<h3>Power of circumstances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:27\">MAT 7:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:25\">MAT 7:25</a></p>\n<h2>Rain in other imagery</h2>\n<p>Ability to satisfy:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:2\">DEU 32:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:23\">JOB 29:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:6\">PSA 72:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:15\">PRO 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:14\">PRO 25:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">JUD 1:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:23\">PRO 25:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:1\">PRO 26:1</a></p>\n<h2>The rainbow</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:14-Gen9:16\">GEN 9:14–9:16</a> <em>a sign of God's covenant</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:3\">REV 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:1\">REV 10:1</a></p>",
